never do drugs 2 escape ur problems..it only makes em a million times worse..n by drugs i mean everything from dip ( even tho thtd b useless) to acid..i myself have never tried 2 run away from my problems by doin ne kind of drug but i no 2 many ppl who have..i worry abt like 4 peoples lives a day.. due 2 either drinkin problems, smokin problems, coke problems, n pill poppin problems..n im gettin pretty damn tired of it.. it almost makes me wanna light 1 up rite now.. but fuck it.. id never smoke 2 get away from shit..idk wat the point of this is..newayz on a lighter note.. wildsplash was the shit.. n mario is fine as hell..barely got 2 smoke ther.. but we hit these fat girls shit n then i had sum bacardi n then i was happy cuz wed been searchin for weed for a couple hrs.. stole sum kids blunt..cant wait 2 get sum weed next weekend n light tht shit up..been fiendin for like a month.. i just need  a couple good smoke outs n ill b good cant wait till me jared n john go at it..fuckin gunna b a blaze fest..thinkin abt havin all 3 of us match our shit..think ima get sum money n buy a half ounce..idk.. cant wait till 420 even tho its far away.. def cant wait till spring break..plan on bein gone the whole time..looks like its time 2 go back 2 the every day smoke out..lately i smoke like once a month.. n everybody still thinks im like sum huge pothead... i wuddnt say im a pothead..but id say i love maryjane..i just can quit whenever i want..yall can think i cant but idc..i seem 2 b fallin back in2 my old fuck everybody ways..looks like alot of troubles gunna b comin my way soon..i hope not..dunno if i can keep my cool for 2 much longer tho..it seems like im constantly depressed..i need 2 fix damn near everything in my life..but its gay cuz its not my fault things went bad...im worried abt my bro..im worried abt myself.. im worried abt my mom.. im worried abt a couple friends.. n im terrified of my future..guess i need 2 work harder then i have been..who cares peace

JULY: Fun to be with. Secretive. Difficult to fathom and to be understood. Quiet unless excited or tensed. Takes pride in oneself. Has reputation. Easily consoled. Honest. Concerned about people's feelings. Tactful. Friendly. Approachable. Emotional temperamental and unpredictable. Moody and easily hurt. Witty and sparkly. Not revengeful. Forgiving but never forgets. Dislikes nonsensical and unnecessary things. Guides others physically and mentally. Sensitive and forms impressions carefully. Caring and loving. Treats others equally. Strong sense of sympathy. Wary and sharp. Judges people through observations. Hardworking. No difficulties in studying. Loves to be alone. Always broods about the past and the old friends. Likes to be quiet. Homely person. Waits for friends. Never looks for friends. Not aggressive unless provoked. Prone to having stomach and dieting problems. Loves to be loved. Easily hurt but takes long to recover

Evaluation/ corrections: im quiet unless excitied or tensed sumtimes..other times im just alwayz loud or unquiet.. i take pride in myself strongly..but try 2 fix the problems in myself tht i find..i have a reputation for bein a stoner...but thts not the case..im extremely easily consoled..unless im mad but even then i am.. im brutally honest usually.. im constantly concerned of ppls feelings.. tact is my middle name.. im friendly and approachable 99% of the time.. im very emotional can b quite tempermental and unpredictable.. sumtimes im moody n i can b easily hurt but i never show it.. witty and sparkly for sure.. revenge is not sumthin i usually aim for.. i do forgive but i NEVER forget.. i dislike nonsensical and unnecessary things..but i think most things make sense and r necessary like being stupid..i try 2 guide ppl mentally n physically but dont alwayz do a good job..i do form impressions carefully.. im very caring and loving.. i treat every1 equal until i feel u dont deserve 2 b treated the same as every1 else( as in i dont like u.. therfore ill just ignore ur ass) im sympathetic but not alwayz..i try 2 be tho.im wary as hell n sharp as a tac..i only judge by observations.. i work hard most the time..like if i feel sumthin shudd b done ill do it 2 the best of my ability..sumtimes i cant concentrate on studyin but thts only when i feel studying is unneccessary..(most the time)  i love being alone but i also love bein in big company.. i brood of the past and old friends with my every whim i can never stop missing sum1 soo much n can never forget the past or let it go.. quietness is gr8 but so is loudness n like regular volume..im very homely n wait on friends all the time.. i dont look for friends i just greet them when i meet them..im not really aggreseive unless u provoke me..i suck at diets n i sumtimes have stomach aches.. i adore being loved..n i can be hurt very easy n i can never seem to recover
